title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from an attached report.
OB: When trying to export data from a table containing highlight/map, an exception is thrown.
SR:
Steps to Reproduce: 
1. Open the attached report. 
2. Navigate to the table that contains the highlight/map. 
3. Attempt to export the data from the table. 
4. Observe that an exception is thrown.
